  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AttributeMetadataHolder<V_ARRAY>
    Helper interface to extend original functionlity (like an instantiation of AttributeDefinition) with AttributeMetadata information.

  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ConfigurationPolicy
    Options for ComponentMetadata#configurationPolicy() property.

    Reference items can be configured with ReferenceConfigurationType.CLAUSEs or OSGi ReferenceConfigurationType.FILTER.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    MetadataValidationException
    A RuntimeException that is thrown if there is a problem with the metadata structure of the component (e.g.: multiple attributes are provided with the same id).
